        All elements of a PWG Raster header as described in section 4.3 of PWG-5102.4.

        Parameters:
        duplex - True if printing two-sided.
        pageSizeX - Media width in points.
        pageSizeY - Media height in points.
        tumble - True if two-sided printing should be flipped along the short-edge.
        width - Full-bleed page width in pixels.
        height - Full-bleed page height in pixels.
        imageBoxLeft - Left position of non-blank area in pixels, if image box is known.
        imageBoxTop - Top position of non-blank area in pixels, if image box is known.
        imageBoxRight - Right position of non-blank area in pixels, if image box is known.
        imageBoxBottom - Bottom position of non-blank area in pixels, if image box is known.
        alternatePrimary - An sRGB color field containing 24 bits of color data. Default: WHITE
        vendorIdentifier - USB vendor identification number or 0.
        vendorData - Octets containing 0-1088 bytes of vendor-specific data.
        See Also:
        PWG-5102.4
